# Next.js Best Practices for Windsurf

## Architecture
- Server Components by default — `'use client'` at leaf level only
- Data fetching in Server Components, not useEffect
- Server Actions = mutations only

## SEO
- metadataBase in root layout
- viewport separate from metadata export  
- generateMetadata() for dynamic pages
- Canonical URL on every page
- JSON-LD structured data

## Performance
- next/image with explicit dimensions and sizes attribute
- priority prop only on LCP image
- next/font, never external font links
- next/script with afterInteractive for analytics
- Promise.all for parallel data fetching
- dynamic() imports for heavy components
- No barrel file imports

## Caching (Next.js 16)
- 'use cache' + cacheTag() + cacheLife()
- updateTag() after mutations
- Suspense for dynamic content

## Core Web Vitals
- LCP < 2.5s, INP < 200ms, CLS < 0.1
